<br>
-Shaman<br>
-Wizard<br>
-bards<br>
<br>
necros, as i heard, arent, ask me why? i dunno, just know that shaman, with nice disease and poison based DoTs, slow, haste,... make some hard mofo to beat on combats <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
